<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4408132>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–6. Dorsal habitus. 1) Lathroeus oreoderoides, holotype. 2) Alcidion interrogationis, holotype. 3) Lathroeus immaculatus, holotype male. 4) Alcidion simillimum, holotype. 5) Alcidion decoratum, holotype male. 6) Lathroeus mysticus, lectotype. Figures 1, 2, and 6 by the late Jesus Santiago Moure; figures 4, 5 by Steven W. Lingafelter; figure 3, from the original description." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4408132/files/figure.png" .
